msgctxt "talk01"
msgid ""
"Discovery Log: Day One\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I come to this snowy mountain intending\n"
"to find the <1.se_co>ancient shrine <2.re_co>that was\n"
"written about in an old text.\n"
"\"The <3.se_co>shrine <4.re_co>slumbers near the pedestal\n"
"on a snowy Gerudo peak.\"\n"
"\n"
"I believe I've arrived at the <5.se_co>pedestal<6.re_co>\n"
"mentioned in the passage.<7.pa><8.ch>"
msgstr ""

