msgctxt "talk03"
msgid ""
"Discovery Log: Day... I've lost count.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I can feel that I'm a hair's breadth away\n"
"from unlocking the secrets hidden within\n"
"the <1.se_co>pedestal<2.re_co>.\n"
"I'm certain that \"<3.se_co>casting<4.re_co>\" and "
"\"<5.se_co>cold<6.re_co>\"\n"
"refer to using a specific type of <7.se_co>shadow<8.re_co>.\n"
"\n"
"But I've run out of food entirely, and I\n"
"doubt now that I ever had the tools to\n"
"do the job...whatever they might be.<9.ch>"
